Package: gopb
Title: GOPB Data Toolkit
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jackson", "Bolos", , "jjbolos@utah.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Internal toolkit offering convenient functions to simplify and streamline
    common data acquisition and integration tasks
    in the Utah Governor's Office of Planning & Budget.
    These include user-friendly interactions with the
    COBI, Budget Builder, and Vantage systems.
